<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f2f5f7; color: #333333; }
        .email-wrapper { width: 100%; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .email-card { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e8ee; box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); }
        .email-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #006633, #004d26); color: #ffffff; text-align: center; padding: 28px 24px; }
        .email-header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; }
        .email-body { padding: 28px 24px; }
        .email-body p { margin: 0 0 18px; line-height: 1.65; color: #4c5866; }
        .otp-code { display: inline-block; background: #f6fff8; color: #006633; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.25em; padding: 18px 24px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #d9eedb; margin: 8px 0 22px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #006633; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 10px; }
        .footer { font-size: 13px; color: #8f97a3; text-align: center; padding: 24px; border-top: 1px solid #eef1f6; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-card">
            <div class="email-header">
                <h1>Password Reset OTP</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="email-body">
<p>Hi,</p>
                <p>Use this one-time password to reset your Reserva FTIC password:</p>
                <div class="otp-code">{{ otp }}</div>
                <p>Enter it on the site within 10 minutes.</p>
                <p>If you didn't request this, ignore safely.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Reserva FTIC Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
